---
title: Scandi-Style Roast Salmon with Scandi Style Potato Gratin and Pickled Cucumber
description: This week’s festive recipe is inspired by Chef Gabby’s mum (she’s Swedish!) We’ve teamed sweet and delicate honey mustard roast salmon with creamy scandi-style potato gratin for a delicious festive treat.
